Welcome to Robert Hawks Auction Company

Robert Hawks Auction Company is a full service auction agency with a staff of expertly trained auctioneers ready to assist you. Founded in 1983, our Company has an incredible client base from which to draw. Our vast experience in the areas of Real Estate, Oil Field Equipment, Farm Equipment, Antiques, Classic Cars, Shop Tools, Business Liquidations, Estates...from Modern to Antique Furnishings, Guns and Jewelry - puts us a step above the rest and delivers optimum result to you!

To ensure a successful auction, it is essential to have your property displayed in an appealing manner that will encourage the bidders to buy. Our trained staff has a proven track record of providing the best possible presentation available for each and every auction performed, assuring the best possible results.

Before an auction is conducted, we start by promoting and advertising through numerous media. Flyers are mailed directly to our extensive computerized mailing list of all past auction buyers as well as potential buyers suited for your merchandise. To provide best results, we also advertise in area newspapers and applicable trade journals when possible. We have an excellent history of bringing buyers and sellers together to assure your property sells for the maximum dollar amount.

Real Estate is fast becoming the most common type of property available at auctions. Real Estate has been sold at auctions over the past century, and is now accepted practice in the business. In view of the inconvenience and time involved in listing property and maintaining that property until a buyer comes along, selling at auction not only eliminates the "waiting game" and maintenance expense, but you determine the day your property will be sold and closed. In many cases, property sold in auction will result in a higher selling price than traditional sales techniques, yielding higher profits. Our staff of licensed Real Estate Professionals will assist in determining fair market appraisal for your property and ensure the best possible price for your property!

Our staff of experienced auctioneers offer a down to earth approach with our clients. We discuss all financial matters beforehand and won't surprise you with a "miscellaneous" charge on your settlement statement. We offer the best personal service and attention to our clients...that's why they keep coming back, again and again.

We have briefly explained the services available with Robert Hawks Auction Company, please feel free to call or e-mail us for additional information. We offer Auction Consultations at no cost or obligation!
